Directory Contents - doc/

Directory Contents

  html/
    An HTML version of Eggdrop's documentation generated from the
    Sphinx source. Open index.html in a web browser to view.

  man1/
    Unix man page files for Eggdrop.

  settings/
    Configuration file documentation for all settings, modules, and
    capabilities.

  sphinx_source/
    Sphinx source files used to generate the HTML documentation.

  modules/
    Module-specific documentation.

GETTING STARTED

  ABOUT
    Information about Eggdrop, its history, and basic requirements.

  COMPILE-GUIDE
    Instructions for building Eggdrop with Meson on various operating
    systems. Start here if you're having build issues.

  INSTALL
    Quick start guide for basic setup and installation.

CONFIGURATION AND USAGE

  eggdrop.toml
    Reference for all configuration settings in TOML format.

  tcl-commands.doc
    Complete documentation on Eggdrop Tcl commands available to
    scripters.

  twitch-tcl-commands.doc
    Tcl commands specific to the Twitch module.

FEATURES AND CAPABILITIES

  TLS
    Documentation on TLS/SSL support (version 1.2 and 1.3). Includes
    certificate generation and authentication.

  IPv6
    Information about IPv6 support and how to use IPv6 addresses in
    Eggdrop.

  IRCv3
    Documentation on IRCv3 capabilities supported by Eggdrop.

  ACCOUNTS
    Information on tracking user accounts and authentication in Eggdrop.

  PBKDF2
    Documentation on modern password hashing using PBKDF2. Covers
    migration from older hashing methods.

USER AND BOT MANAGEMENT

  USERS
    Explanation of Eggdrop's user database and user flags.

  BOTNET
    Guide to setting up and managing Eggdrops linked in a botnet.

  BANS
    Documentation on channel ban, exempt, and invite lists.

  PARTYLINE
    Information about the Eggdrop partyline interface and DCC chat.

SCRIPTING

  FIRST-SCRIPT
    Beginner's guide to writing Tcl scripts for Eggdrop.

  AUTOSCRIPTS
    Documentation on Eggdrop's auto-script functionality.

ADVANCED TOPICS

  TRICKS
    Advanced tips and configuration tweaks for Eggdrop.

  PATCH-HOWTO
    Guide to creating and submitting patches to Eggdrop.

  BUG-REPORT
    Bug report form and instructions for reporting issues on GitHub.

LEGAL

